OL,3,CAlmost 900 people sign up to new
OL,4,C'MyCesspit Portal'
OL,6,FA free online service in Guernsey
OL,7,Fwhich allows people to check when
OL,8,Ftheir next cesspit collection is due
OL,9,Fhas seen a reduction in the number of
OL,10,Fcall queries.
OL,12,F'MyCesspit Portal' was rolled out by
OL,13,FGuernsey Water just before Christmas
OL,14,Fand has seen almost 900 customers sign
OL,15,Fup in the first month.
OL,17,FBusiness Change Manager Andrea Simpson
OL,18,Fsays: "People are taking advantage of
OL,19,Fgetting the information about their
OL,20,Fcesspit directly into their hands -
OL,21,Fright where it belongs."
