OL,3,CAlmost 900 people sign up to new
OL,4,C'MyCesspit Portal'
OL,6,FAccount holders who opt in also
OL,7,Freceive automatic email notifications
OL,8,Fwhen their cesspit has been emptied or
OL,9,Fif there was an access issue.
OL,11,FAndrea adds: "We heard customers loud
OL,12,Fand clear that not having any way of
OL,13,Fknowing if their pit had been
OL,14,Fcollected was a source of deep
OL,15,Ffrustration."
OL,17,FGuernsey Water says more functions
OL,18,Fwill be added to the portal this year,
OL,19,Fincluding the ability to rearrange
OL,20,Fcollections online and service updates
OL,21,Fin case of disruption.
